Age group dependent 7-Day Incidences for Germany

based on weekly data published by RKI

Wolfgang Vollmer

2021-06-08

Data source: the age group specific incidence data is provided weekly, every Tuesday evening RKI - COVID-19-Flle nach Altersgruppe und Meldewoche.

Attention: unfortunately RKI is changing more or less frequently table sheet 7-Tages-Inzidenz name and even sometimes rownames of column Altersgruppe.
